{
"#useparam"
:
true
,
"#name"
:
{
"x telegram"
:
null
,
"cn"
:
"使用 Telegram 群机器人发送消息"
,
"en"
:
"Send messages using a Telegram group bot"
}
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"使用 x telegram 向你的 Telegram 群或频道发送消息。首次使用需要配置群机器人的 token。"
,
"en"
:
"Use x telegram send messages to your Telegram group or channel. The first use requires configuring bot token."
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"en"
:
"Instructions for get Telegram bot token:  https://core.telegram.org/bots#how-do-i-create-a-bot\n- Interactive env use `x telegram init` to initialize configuration. The configure will be saved locally.\n- Run command `x telegram --cfg token=<token>` to add token.\n"
,
"cn"
:
"Telegram bot token 获取指引: https://core.telegram.org/bots#how-do-i-create-a-bot\n- 交互环境中可使用 `x telegram init` 进行初始化配置，配置信息将存放于本地保存\n- 亦可运行命令 `x telegram --cfg token=<token>` 添加 token\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x telegram --cfg token=<token>"
,
"cn"
:
"设置群机器人的 token"
,
"en"
:
"Set the group bot's token"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x telegram send --text \"x-cmd v1.0 released successfully\""
,
"cn"
:
"发送文本消息到 Telegram 群"
,
"en"
:
"Send text type messages to Telegram group"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x telegram send --text --chat \"@channelusername\" \"x-cmd v1.0 released successfully\""
,
"cn"
:
"发送文本消息到 Telegram 频道"
,
"en"
:
"Send text type messages to Telegram channel"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x telegram send --image --chat \"-967810017\" --file_path ./a.png"
,
"cn"
:
"发送 a.png 图片到 Telegram 群"
,
"en"
:
"Send a.png images to Telegram group"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x telegram react --runner repl"
,
"cn"
:
"启动交互式指令模式，将收到的消息作为命令执行并返回结果"
,
"en"
:
"Start interactive REPL mode, executing messages as commands and returning output"
}
]
,
"#subcmd:config"
:
[
"init"
,
"--cfg"
,
"--cur"
]
,
"send"
:
{
"#subcmd:Multimedia"
:
[
"--file"
,
"--image"
,
"--video"
,
"--audio"
,
"--voice"
,
"--animation"
,
"--video_note"
]
,
"#subcmd:Location"
:
[
"--venue"
,
"--location"
]
,
"#subcmd:Poll"
:
[
"--poll"
,
"--stop_poll"
]
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"使用 Telegram 群机器人发送消息（等同于 x telegram bot send）"
,
"en"
:
"Send messages using a Telegram group bot (equivalent to `x telegram bot send`)"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x telegram send --text \"x-cmd v1.0 released successfully\""
,
"cn"
:
"发送文本消息到 Telegram 群"
,
"en"
:
"Send text type messages to Telegram group"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x telegram send --text --chat \"@channelusername\" \"x-cmd v1.0 released successfully\""
,
"cn"
:
"发送文本消息到 Telegram 频道"
,
"en"
:
"Send text type messages to Telegram channel"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x telegram send --image --chat \"-967810017\" --file_path ./a.png"
,
"cn"
:
"发送 a.png 图片到 Telegram 群"
,
"en"
:
"Send a.png images to Telegram group"
}
]
,
